These are some of the best streets to spot incredible art:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Plazoleta Chorro de Quevedo<\/li><li>Calle Del Embudo<\/li><li>From Calle Del Embudo, follow to the end of Carrera 2<\/li><li>Carrera 3<\/li><li>Calle 12f<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/79142&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25130135\/bogota-colombia-3.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25130135\/bogota-colombia-3-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25130135\/bogota-colombia-3-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"15 Things to do in Bogota, Colombia\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-3-cerro-monserrate\">3. Cerro Monserrate<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Bogota sits in the shadow of the majestic Monserrate, a beautiful mountain just outside the city that stands over 3000 meters tall. For those looking for a bit of adventure and exertion, you can hike to the top of the peak. However, be aware that this can take between 2-4 hours, so take a reusable water bottle with plenty of water. It&#x2019;s safe as guards are posted throughout the hike for safety but keep in mind that you can only enter the trail in the morning.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tips to travel plastic-free!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18104301\/bogota-colombia-25.jpg\" alt=\"Cerro Monserrate things to do bogota\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Cerro Monserrate things to do bogota\" class=\"wp-image-80385 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18104301\/bogota-colombia-25.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18104301\/bogota-colombia-25-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18104301\/bogota-colombia-25-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18104301\/bogota-colombia-25-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/u