white stripes, looking like a piece of candy among the city&#x2019;s roofs.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/bogota-hotels-all\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Bogota.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18135612\/bogota-colombia-36.jpg\" alt=\"bogota Santuario Nuestra Se&#xF1;ora del Carmen\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bogota Santuario Nuestra Se&#xF1;ora del Carmen\" class=\"wp-image-80434 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18135612\/bogota-colombia-36.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18135612\/bogota-colombia-36-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18135612\/bogota-colombia-36-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18135612\/bogota-colombia-36-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18135612\/bogota-colombia-36-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18135612\/bogota-colombia-36-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18135612\/bogota-colombia-36-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/stati