 restaurant with a fun industrial-style interior hidden down a small alley. They do great pizzas, delicious cocktails and often have live music while you eat!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46.jpg\" alt=\"restaurant bogota madre\"><\/noscript><img width=\"251\" height=\"338\" alt=\"restaurant bogota madre\" class=\"wp-image-80748 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1425px) 100vw, 1425px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46.jpg 1425w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-445x600.jpg 445w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-601x810.jpg 601w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-251x338.jpg 251w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-121x163.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-134x180.jpg 134w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-570x768.jpg 570w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-760x1024.jpg 760w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-802x1080.jpg 802w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-1069x1440.jpg 1069w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25120549\/bogota-colombia-46-300x404.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourha