rong> If you&#x2019;re not in Bogota on a Sunday, head for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/place\/Pasaje+Rivas\/@4.5994309,-74.0803995,17z\/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x8e3f9909cb6be503:0x5abee48a710c21cd!8m2!3d4.5994325!4d-74.0782133\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pasaje Rivas<\/a>, a small hidden market in La Candelaria. You&#x2019;ll discover beautiful handicrafts here, from handmade hammocks to wooden furniture.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33.jpg\" alt=\"market bogota\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"297\" alt=\"market bogota\" class=\"wp-image-80424 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-800x528.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-1080x713.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-450x297.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-163x108.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-273x180.jpg 273w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-768x507.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-1024x676.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-1440x950.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-300x198.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-600x396.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-150x99.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18134556\/bogota-colombia-33.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-10-salt-cathedral-zipaquira\">10. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/bogota-zipaquira\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Salt Cathedral, Zipaquira<\/a>&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Just 1 hour from Bogota is the fascinating Salt Cathedral of Zipaquira. Underneath the ground, discover the salt mine tunnels and a cathedral carved down to a depth of 200 meters. The massive space is lit with neon blue light to highlight the alcoves, stones, and pews. In fact, people still attend church services here; it&#x2019;s a completely unique religious site!<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"43262P1,7557P7,23817P9\" data-vi-campaign=\"things-to-do-bogota-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-11-botero-museum\">11. Botero Museum&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Botero Museum is a free art museum in Bogota home to multiple modern art exhibitions. It&#x2019;s named after Fernando Botero, the most famous Colombian artist (from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/medellin-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Medellin<\/a>) renowned for his colorful, funny, and large paintings. His artwork is totally unique, painting and sculpting humans with proportions far bigger than the average! There is even Botero&#x2019;s version of the Mona Lisa. You will love it! You can see his work displayed all over the world, in major cities like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/things-to-do-madrid\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Madrid<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/singapore\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Singapore<\/a>.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Opening times:<\/strong> 9 AM &#x2013; 7 PM (closed on Tuesdays. Open 10 AM &#x2013; 5 PM on Sundays)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/19132904\/bogota-colombia-43.jpg\" alt=\"bogota botero museum\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bogota bot