\/bogota-colombia-1-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/15121654\/bogota-colombia-1-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/15121654\/bogota-colombia-1-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/15121654\/bogota-colombia-1-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/15121654\/bogota-colombia-1-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/15121654\/bogota-colombia-1-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/15121654\/bogota-colombia-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-13-gold-museum\">13. Gold Museum<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Museo del Oro (Gold Museum) is a top thing to do in Bogota. Home to over 34,000 gold items, it&#x2019;s no surprise that this museum has been named one of the greatest in the world. Each piece tells an incredible historical story, with many coming from the rituals and practices of indigenous communities.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/bogota-hotels-all\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Bogota.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20.jpg\" alt=\"bogota gold museum colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"263\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bogota gold museum colombia\" class=\"wp-image-80290 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1496px) 100vw, 1496px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20.jpg 1496w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-468x600.jpg 468w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-631x810.jpg 631w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-263x338.jpg 263w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-127x163.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-140x180.jpg 140w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-598x768.jpg 598w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-798x1024.jpg 798w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-842x1080.jpg 842w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-1122x1440.jpg 1122w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-300x385.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-600x770.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-150x193.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15140432\/bogota-colombia-20.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Taking an audio tour of the Gold Museum is possible, but you don&#x2019;t necessarily need to, as each piece of art has Spanish and English descriptions.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Entry Fee:<\/strong> 4000 COP (~ 1 USD)&#xA0; or 9000 COP for an audio tour. On Sundays, the Gold Museum is free.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-14-visit-a-local-coffee-plantation\">14. Visit a Local Coffee Plantation&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Colombian coffee is widely known as some of the best in the world, so make the most of being in Bogota by visiting one of the many coffee plantations up in the surrounding hills. Not only will you learn all about the growth, production, and sale of coffee, you&#x2019;ll get to try the coffee too! <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>For more coffee visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/salento-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Salento in Colombia<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25121011\/SA72731.jpg\" alt=\"coffee plantation\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"coffee plantation\" class=\"wp-image-80756 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25121011\/SA72731.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25121011\/SA72731-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25121011\/SA72731-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25121011\/SA72731-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25121011\/SA72731-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25121011\/SA72731-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25121011\/SA72731-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25121011\/SA72731-768x512.j