ia, which turns into a nightclub after dinner. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Our favorite restaurants in Bogota:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>De Una Travel (perfect spot for lunch)<\/li><li>Varietale (delicious coffee and cakes)<\/li><li>Quinua Y Amaranto (vegetarian local food)<\/li><li>Madre (hidden gem in the center of Bogota)<\/li><li>Enchiladas La Candelaria (mexican)<\/li><li>Nativa Arte y Comida Natural (vegan food)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13.jpg\" alt=\"restaurants bogota colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"restaurants bogota colombia\" class=\"wp-image-80269 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/15131513\/bogota-colombia-13-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.