\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-around-bogota\">Getting Around Bogota<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Bogota is a massive city so you&#x2019;ll need to take public transport to visit all the sights. The good news is that the bus system is super cheap, as well as the local taxis and Uber. Bicycles and buses have their own lane, making it faster to get around this way. If you&#x2019;re planning on cycling, we recommend taking a bike tour to learn as much as possible and travel safely around the city.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679.jpg\" alt=\"bogota bus\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bogota bus\" class=\"wp-image-80407 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/18130347\/SA70679-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinou